lead_paragraph: Tyler Seguin and Patrick Sharp scored back-to-back goals to start the shootout and the Dallas Stars ended a season-high three-game losing streak with a 2-1 win over the Winnipeg Jets on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Stars Beat Jets 2-1 in Shootout to End 3-Game Losing Streak
